    fix(vendor): fix PathBuf import cfg for Windows builds
    
    PathBuf is only used in Unix(PathBuf) variant which is #[cfg(unix)],
    so guard the import with #[cfg(unix)] instead of #[cfg(feature = "runtime")]
    to avoid unused-import error on Windows.
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>

